-- GAG2 Fruit Scanner v4.7
-- Changes from v4.6:
--   * REAL value formula extracted from ReplicatedStorage.SharedModules.FruitValueCalc
--   * Size exponent 2.65 (default), 1.9 Mushroom, 1.75 Bamboo
--   * Diminishing returns past size 5 (knee), tail exponent 1.5
--   * Single-harvest crops get scaled mutation bonus: 1 + (m-1)*0.15
--   * Carrot enforced minimum value of 4
--   * Removed bogus Dragon's Breath power-curve math (it's just base*size^2.65)
--   * Mutation multipliers verified against MutationData submodules
--   * Aurora "?" flag removed (1.5x is confirmed correct)
-- ============================================================
